    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Travel Agent - Minimal Context Given\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a travel agent by giving a simple, unstructured prompt to see how AI makes recommendations without any specific details or examples.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a basic prompt like the one below, or a similar one related to family vacations.\r\n\r\n>Recommend a family vacation destination.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how useful or generic the recommendation is.",
